## AGENTS DOMAIN MODULE — IMPLEMENTATION PATTERNS REFERENCE

Based on analysis of the Brain codebase, here are the key patterns and structures for implementing a new `agents/` domain module for CRUD operations on agent configurations.

### 1. SCHEMA PATTERNS

#### Agent Table Definition
```sql
DEFINE TABLE agent SCHEMAFULL;
DEFINE FIELD agent_type ON agent TYPE string 
  ASSERT $value IN ['code_agent', 'architect', 'management', 'design_partner', 'observer', 'chat_agent', 'mcp'];
DEFINE FIELD model ON agent TYPE option<string>;
DEFINE FIELD description ON agent TYPE option<string>;
